<section>
<id root="9AFBE48A-35BB-0104-B17A-D7692381B975" />
<code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" codeSystemVersion="LOINC" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION" />
<title mediaType="text/x-hl7-title+xml"><content styleCode="bold">Visual Inspection</content></title>
<text><paragraph>Parenteral drug products should be inspected visually for
particulate matter and discoloration prior to administration, whenever solution
and container permit.</paragraph></text>
<effectiveTime value="20070623" />
</section>
</component>
</section>
