<section>
<id root="D1169DA7-8A32-3014-B810-5C08EE6140C0" />
<code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" codeSystemName="LOINC" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION" />
<title mediaType="text/x-hl7-title+xml">HOW SUPPLIED</title>
<effectiveTime value="20070623" />
<component>
<section>
<id root="2E7E1253-EA1A-8FC5-9363-432D4E002527" />
<code />
<title mediaType="text/x-hl7-title+xml">Identity</title>
<text><paragraph>No. 1000, GLOFIL<sup>&#174;</sup>-125 is a clear, colorless,
sterile, and nonpyrogenic solution available as a 4 mL vial. It is supplied
in a concentration of approximately 1 mg/mL sodium iothalamate (range is 0.5&#8211;2.0
mg sodium iothalamate per mL), with a radioactivity concentration of 250 to
300 &#956;Ci/mL at the time of calibration. Benzyl alcohol 0.9%, is added as
a preservative. Sodium bicarbonate and hydrochloric acid are added for pH
adjustment.  The calibration and expiration dates are shown on the label.</paragraph></text>
<effectiveTime value="20070623" />
</section>
</component>
<component>
<section>
<id root="5DB37B62-7B7E-2F0A-8553-ABDB34C42627" />
<code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" codeSystemName="LOINC" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION" />
<title mediaType="text/x-hl7-title+xml"><content styleCode="bold">Storage</content></title>
<text><paragraph>Refrigerate the product upon receipt at 2&#176;C to 8&#176;C.</paragraph></text>
<effectiveTime value="20070623" />
</section>
</component>
